SimonShield
===========
A simple Arduino shield to build a Simon game.

This project contains the working material for a two day secondary school
Arduino workshop.

Directories:
============
|
+-Hardware              - Everything needed to build the SimonShield shield
|
+-Software              - Source files of the SimonShield shields firmware
|
+-Workshop              - Workshop materials

